description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Solent NHS Trust Estates Premises Team in &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Portsmouth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;are seeking an enthusiastic and customer focussed Reception Supervisor. This role is an exciting opportunity to join a forward-thinking Trust and Premises Team at a time of exciting change within the NHS.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;This role will see the successful candidate based at St Marys Hospital in Portsmouth, but supporting buildings across the Portsmouth and South East Hants Health System. The successful candidate will be Line Manager for reception teams based on the St Marys site. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidate will be a highly motivated individual capable of working independently and as part of a wider team. They will be approachable and highly customer focussed and take pride in the attractive appearance and smooth operation of Estates Site Operations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Under the guidance of the Estates Premises Manager they will support the operation of buildings and development of a customer focused highly utilised environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please contact Kim Barnes on kim.barnes@solent.nhs.uk for further information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that should this post attract sufficient interest, we may choose to close at an earlier date. We strongly suggest that you apply at an early stage.&lt;strong&gt;If we have not contacted you within four weeks of the closing date of this post, please presume that you have not been selected.&lt;/strong&gt;Candidates selected for interview will be contacted within 2-3 weeks; therefore you should check your emails regularly including junk mail folders.&lt;/p&gt;
